{
  "stem": "18056.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 251.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would wake us up, go to the bathroom, take a-- a shower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they had water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ice-cold water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ice cold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would wash there-- or if they didn't have a shower, we wouldn't wash.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We wouldn't wash sometimes for six, seven weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And get some food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would give us the piece of bread and some chicory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Instead of coffee, it was chicory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then stay outside until the-- the master, the big guy will come and make sure that we are all out there, so on the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he would let us-- [INAUDIBLE] was raining and snowing or whatever it was, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He-- they had to count us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They count us again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they would go in and have discussions over us and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyways, this is how it happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We got to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was, like-- at the beginning, it was two shifts, 12 hours a shift.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we would work from 7:00 to 7:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, we would have to walk about a-- an hour, hour and a half, to-- to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we would work 12 hours, then come home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we came home, we had to pick up the soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then after a while, they changed the-- the idea of having the bread in the morning, so they gave it to you in the evening.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The soup and a piece of bread, that's for next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "To give you an idea, as I said before, that we did in Auschwitz, we got two people a bread, and then it became three people a bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "At that time, when the-- about six weeks before the war ended, we got 20 people a bread. 20 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was a slice that thick.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
